排支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1894747\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1894747</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1810669</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n必須先紅後藍，否則中共恐成最後贏家<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1809175\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1809175</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5b5a45b8202f56dd47a73e314e946ce9828e4ef6","tid":1913021,"uid":351361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:24:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0c2ab51029f2a1343f11051db1e5c777ea8f6a9e","tid":1913021,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T16:52:25.000Z","msg":"佢地似識架喎"}]}